1996 and 2000 US Presidential Election Data for Florida Counties

1996 and 2000 election outcomes in each Florida county by candidate.

florida

Format

A data frame with 67 rows and 7 variables:

county

character: county name

Clinton96

integer: Clinton’s votes in 1996

Dole96

integer: Dole’s votes in 1996

Perot96

integer: Perot’s votes in 1996

Bush00

integer: Bush’s votes in 2000

Gore00

integer: Gore’s votes in 2000

Buchanan00

integer: Buchanan’s votes in 2000

Details

See QSS Table 4.6.

References

Imai, Kosuke. 2017. Quantitative Social Science: An Introduction. Princeton University Press. URL.
